<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>아이디 찾기</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-KK94CHFLLe+nY2dmCWGMq91rCGa5gtU4mk92HdvYe+M/SXH301p5ILy+dN9+nJOZ" crossorigin="anonymous">
</head>
<body>
<div class="container" >
    <div class="container" style="background-color : #eee" style = "border-radius: 10%">
        <div class="mb-3">
            <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 50px" class="mb-5">아이디 찾기</p>
        </div>
        <form action="/findemail" method="POST" class="mb-3">
            <label for="name" class="form-label">이름:</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" class="form-control" required /><br />
            <div>
                <label for="question" class="form-label">질문 선택:</label>
                <select name="question" id="question" class="form-control">
                    <option value="1">당신이 태어난 곳은 어디입니까?</option>
                    <option value="2">출신 초등학교는 어디인가요?</option>
                    <option value="3">감명깊게 본 영화는 어떤 영화인가요?</option>
                </select>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-3">
                <label for="answer" class="form-label">답변:</label>
                <input type="text" name="answer" id="answer" class="form-control" required />
            </div>
            <div class="mt-3 mb-3">
                <input type="submit" value="이메일 찾기">
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>
</div>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-ENjdO4Dr2bkBIFxQpeoTz1HIcje39Wm4jDKdf19U8gI4ddQ3GYNS7NTKfAdVQSZe" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>
